<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-br">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title><%= titulo %></title>

    <meta property="og:title" content="<%= titulo %>">
    <meta property="og:image" content="<%= capa %>">
    <meta property="og:type" content="video.other">
    
    <meta property="og:video" content="<%= magicUrl %>">
    <meta property="og:video:url" content="<%= magicUrl %>">
    <meta property="og:video:secure_url" content="<%= magicUrl %>">
    <meta property="og:video:type" content="video/mp4">

    <style>
        body { margin: 0; background: #000; height: 100vh; display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center; justify-content: center; color: white; font-family: sans-serif; text-align: center; }
        .logo { color: #E50914; font-weight: 900; font-size: 24px; margin-bottom: 20px; }
        .msg { max-width: 80%; line-height: 1.6; }
        .btn { background: #E50914; color: white; padding: 12px 25px; border-radius: 5px; text-decoration: none; font-weight: bold; margin-top: 20px; display: inline-block; }
        .sub-btn { color: #aaa; font-size: 12px; margin-top: 20px; display: block; text-decoration: none; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <div class="logo">CINE RAVE</div>
    
    <div class="msg">
        <h2>Modo Compatibilidade</h2>
        <p>O Rave deve abrir o vídeo automaticamente.</p>
        <p>Se nada acontecer, clique no botão abaixo:</p>
        
        <a href="<%= magicUrl %>" class="btn">ABRIR VÍDEO AGORA</a>
        
        <a href="/" class="sub-btn">Voltar ao Menu</a>
    </div>

</body>
</html>